{"tid":279260,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"今次熱狗件事，其實反映左郁撚都只係食人血饅頭","createTime":"2017-06-11T06:32:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-11T09:44:46.000Z","uid":25250,"like":4,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d6eba88bccf3cf351a7aa7837ab8a8e558bf26d9","tid":279260,"uid":25250,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T06:32:38.000Z","msg":"你估佢做咁多年政客唔知國師套永續基本法廢咩<br />\n你覺得佢真係一開始就唔帶眼識人覺得鳩達真心為香港咩<br />\n<br />\n係，你可以話全香港既政客都食人血饅頭<br />\n係，我認同郁撚係深知立法會玩法既前議員<br />\n<br />\n但係佢真係好有人格品德咩，唔覺囉<br />\n歡迎郁撚支持者插死我"},{"pid":"7371409c9f4ad113d5949973316b4e6e99a82b98","tid":279260,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T06:36:11.000Z","msg":"唔需要抹黑我係熱狗或者建制<br />\n我就係覺得郁撚根本由一開始就扮曬野"},{"pid":"a37166c2d8c405d208005906589211e28ea3627f","tid":279260,"uid":43696,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T06:41:12.000Z","msg":"熱狗水泥隊不如停啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你班撚樣穩定番自己班弱智支持者<br />\n靜番排咪無野啦<br />\n<br />\n而家咁樣愈黎愈多人反感"},{"pid":"1061a1d0d2aeee763ef15660c67a2d613273739c","tid":279260,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T06:50:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>熱狗水泥隊不如停啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你班撚樣穩定番自己班弱智支持者<br />\n靜番排咪無野啦<br />\n<br />\n而家咁樣愈黎愈多人反感</blockquote><br />\n你追下post先 我隔離新西post自叫人投李卓人咋 水泥隊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61d877cde213eb0279594b08d5e36ffefd707dcf","tid":279260,"uid":25250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T06:52:00.000Z","msg":"有冇人留意到熱普城支持者集中係天元屯？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/278682?ref=ios\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/278682?ref=ios</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"643a4465f71ecd28aaf5524911c221c592369c9b","tid":279260,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-11T07:00:51.000Z","msg":"其實我都講過毓民同熱狗一